relevant to what's going on in this room.

07:27.600 --> 07:29.830
Believe me, what I've been
dreaming about,

07:29.902 --> 07:32.063
believe me, it's relevant.

07:32.138 --> 07:34.629
- Well...
- Good morning.

07:34.707 --> 07:36.641
Sorry I'm late.

07:36.709 --> 07:38.700
Me and Laura figured
you were early.

07:39.879 --> 07:42.074
Shall we get started?

07:42.148 --> 07:44.673
