as a suspect.

11:33.393 --> 11:36.954
Boy, that's really funny.

11:37.029 --> 11:38.963
Funny.

11:49.275 --> 11:51.334
Mr. Zimmer.

11:51.411 --> 11:53.345
I'm Detective Kelly.
This is Detective Sipowicz.

11:53.413 --> 11:56.041
- I know this is a hard time for you.
- She never hurt anyone.

11:56.115 --> 11:59.016
- Not as long as I knew her.
