12:21.707 --> 12:25.165
Did you notice any other
cars around you? Makes? Drivers?

12:25.244 --> 12:28.372
- No.
- Anybody driving erratically or anything?

12:28.448 --> 12:30.643
- No.
- Where were you headed?

12:30.716 --> 12:36.382
I was... headed to my mother-in-law's
to pick up the baby.

12:36.456 --> 12:38.481
God, what am
