when they go before the grand jury.

14:36.208 --> 14:38.199
Once the medical report is in,
I can testify...

14:38.277 --> 14:40.370
Is that supposed
to reassure me?

14:40.446 --> 14:43.438
I can't be
at the late arraignment,

14:43.516 --> 14:45.848
but I will definitely
see Nathan later.

14:45.918 --> 14:47.852
If you get to talk
to him in court,

14:47.920 --> 14:51.788
please tell him to calm down
'cause it's only gonna make it worse.

14:51.857 --> 14:54.417
He left yesterday morning...

14:54.493 --> 14:56.552
