15:22.355 --> 15:25.017
- Were you around here yesterday?
- Are you on your lunch break?

15:25.091 --> 15:27.025
- Let's go already!
- Thanks.

15:27.093 --> 15:29.994
- Move it!
- This guy with the horn's a pain in the ass.

15:30.062 --> 15:32.257
Come on!

