16:09.468 --> 16:12.130
- Hands on the wheel!
- What the hell are you chasing me for?

16:12.204 --> 16:14.866
Give me your license
and registration.

16:14.940 --> 16:16.874
- What do you want?
- Get over there.

16:16.942 --> 16:19.137
- All right.
- Your license and registration.

16:19.211 --> 16:21.873
- All right.
- Let's see your hands.

16:21.947 --> 16:24.381
Now, we're gonna talk
about that finger right there.

16:24.450 --> 16:27.783
