- Making any progress?

17:37.323 --> 17:39.553
- We'll let you know.
- I hope at least you've ruled me out.

17:39.625 --> 17:41.559
I hope you got that far.

17:41.627 --> 17:44.323
- We'll keep you posted.
- That's great.

17:44.396 --> 17:48.230
