got a three-month-old I got to take care of.

17:48.300 --> 17:51.895
I've got to go through getting
hounded and persecuted by you people.

17:56.876 --> 17:59.367
That's
a natural reaction, right?

17:59.445 --> 18:03.745
- So how come I make this guy a jerk?
- Kelly. Sipowicz.

18:03.816 --> 18:05.750
Give me a minute?

18:14.693 --> 18:16.786
Kelly and Sipowicz,
you know Licalsi and Lucas.

18:16.862 --> 18:18.295
How you doing?

18:18.364 --> 18:21.026
